[0.006, "o", "\u001b[2;37mCompleting commands\u001b[m\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[7mblame   -- Show what revision and author last modified each line of a file\u001b[0m\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\ngrep    -- Print lines matching a pattern\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\nlog     -- Show commit logs\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\nreflog  -- Manage reflog information\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\nrefs    -- Start up in refs view\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\nshow    -- Show various types of objects\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\nstash   -- Start up in stash view\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\nstatus  -- Start up in status view\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[2;37mCompleting files\u001b[m\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[0mAGENTS.md            completers_release/  go.mod               LICENSE              skills/            \u001b[K\r\ncmd/                 compose.yaml         go.sum               pkg/                 staticcheck.conf   \u001b[K\r\ncompleters/          docs/                internal/            README.md                               \u001b[K\r\n\u001b[2;37mCompleting heads\u001b[m\u001b[K\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[0mHEAD                                                                  \u001b[K\r\norigin/HEAD                                                           \u001b[K\r\n                                                                      \u001b[K\r\nFETCH_HEAD                                                            \u001b[K\r\n                                                                      \u001b[K\r\nORIG_HEAD                                                             \u001b[K\r\n\u001b[2m-- zsh: noprefix                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[2m-- Merge pull request #3561 from carapace-sh/update-ghostty-compl..   \u001b[0m\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[JHEAD                                                                  \u001b[J\u001b[J\u001b[23A\u001b[0m\u001b[27m\u001b[24m\r\u001b[6Ctig blame\u001b[K\u001b[1C\r\r\n\u001b[1B\u001b[7mblame   -- Show what revision and author last modified each line of a file\u001b[0m\u001b[K\r\u001b[7mblame   -- Show what revision and author last modified each line of a file\u001b[0m\u001b[K\r\u001bM\u001bM\u001b[0m\u001b[27m\u001b[24m\r\u001b[6Ctig blame\u001b[K\u001b[1C\b\b\b\b\b\bgrep \r\r\n\u001b[1B\u001b[0mblame   -- Show what revision and author last modified each line of a file\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[7mgrep    -- Print lines matching a pattern\u001b[0m\u001b[K\r\u001bM\u001bM\u001bM\u001b[0m\u001b[27m\u001b[24m\r\u001b[6Ctig grep\u001b[K\u001b[1C"]
